"     Boulton DW, Woods DJ, Fawcett JP, et al, &ldquo;The Stability of an Enalapril Maleate Oral Solution Prepared From Tablets,&rdquo;",
"     <i>",
"      Aust J Hosp Pharm",
"     </i>",
"     , 1994, 24(2):151-6.",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Nahata MC, Morosco RS, and Hipple TF, \"Stability of Enalapril Maleate in Three Extemporaneously Prepared Oral Liquids,\"",
"     <i>",
